                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-178-victim1078 t18260914-178-viclabel1029"></join>. The prisoner has been in my employ at different times; I left her in charge of my room on the 28th of July- I went out about two o'clock and returned at six, when she and the articles were gone.</p>
